  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A short 14 day phase 1 study examining 6 monotherapy doses of oral tamoxifen for safety in
      chronic HCV patients who have failed standard treatment of peginterferon and ribavirin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Six different dosages of tamoxifen will be given for 14 days with safety and viral loads
      being measured.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
